Package: dagriculture
Title: Pure Value-Oriented Directed Acyclic Graphs for Task Planning
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("Maximilian Scholz", , , "dev.scholz@mailbox.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Maximilian Scholz [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Maximilian Scholz <dev.scholz@mailbox.org>
Description: A pure, value-oriented directed acyclic graph library for managing
    graph structures, topological dependencies, structural validity, and task
    planning. Graph-modifying operations are immutable and return new graph
    instances.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/sims1253/dagriculture, https://sims1253.github.io/dagriculture/
